# Project Overview

InfiniRewards Documentation is a website built to document the InfiniRewards platform, which introduces the concept of "Token with Utility" - adding programmable logic to both fungible (ERC20) and non-fungible (ERC1155) tokens on StarkNet.

## Tech Stack
- **Next.js**: The project is built using Next.js as the React framework
- **Fumadocs**: Documentation framework used for content organization
- **Tailwind CSS**: Used for styling
- **TypeScript**: The project uses TypeScript for type safety

## Key Files
- Main configuration: [next.config.mjs](mdc:next.config.mjs)
- TypeScript configuration: [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json)
- Source configuration: [source.config.ts](mdc:source.config.ts)
- Project entry point: [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx)
- Documentation content: Stored in [content/docs](mdc:content/docs) directory
